                      </li>
                      <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="mailto:gla@vit.ac.in"><i class="far fa-envelope"></i></a>
                      </li>
    
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </nav>

            <div class="top-upper-layer">

            </div>
            <div class="separator">
                <div class="logo">
                    <img src="images/logo_bg.png" alt="" class="logo-bg">
                    <img src="images/logo_upper.svg" alt="" class="logo-fg">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="particles" id="particles">
                <script type="text/javascript" src="particles.js"></script>
                <script type="text/javascript" src="particle-div.js"></script>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="main">

        <div class="custom-margin">
            <h1 class="custom-h1 mb-4">Capture the Flag</h1>
            <h5 class="mb-4 text-center">Clue-me-in 2.0</h5>
            <% if(alert.length > 0){ %>

                <div class="alert alert-primary alert-dismissible fade show col-lg-6 col-md-8 colo-sm-10 mx-auto" role="alert">
                    <%= alert %>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
              
              <% } %>
            <form name="" method="post" action="/capture/start">
                
                <div class="mb-3 col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Whatsapp number</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" required maxlength="10" minlength="10" autofocus>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3 col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="row">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning my-4 col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-10 mx-auto" id="startgame">Enter event</button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <div class="description">
              <h1 class="text-center my-4">Quick description</h1>
              <h5>Continuing our theme of learning with games, we present an online treasure hunt full of highly intellectual questions, from various genres. 
                The answer of the previous question opens the door to the next. The final answer is the key to win the game. 
                The mind boggling riddles will make this game an engaging activity.</h5>
            </div>

            <div class="event-rules">
              <h1 class="text-center my-4">Rules and instructions</h1>
              <ul>
                <li>The event time is 10:20 PM to 11:05 PM, 15 MAY 2021. You can start filling details at 10:20 PM.</li>
                <li>Enter your Whatsapp number and Full name to start event✨. These details will be reflected in responses.</li>
                <li>After submitting, first clue🧩 will be shown to you.</li>
                <li>You need to type your answer and then click on 'Check Ans'. If your ans is correct✅ 'Submit' button will be enabled. After submitting you will be redirected to next question.</li>
                <li>Answer should be in 'English' language only❕. And it is of one or two words. </li>
                <li>There are total 15 questions in this hunt. You will be given total 45 mins🕒 to solve them.</li>
                <li>Timer will be shown above clues. If timer reaches 00:00, your response will be submitted automatically. But the last answer will not❌ be saved even if it correct.</li>
                <li>If you close the browser by mistake, don't worry✌. Again enter the event, by filling your details. It will continue from the last question where you left. (But not the timer❌. As you know, "Time and Tide Wait for None" 😛)</li>
                <li>Enjoy the event. Best of luck👍</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

       
    </section>

    <section id="footer">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <p>© Copyright <span id="Copyright"></span> GLA_VIT</p>
        </div>
    </section>
